      {% comment %}Steps rendered by JS from metafield or product-handle defaults{% endcomment %}
    </div>
    <p style="margin-top:1.75rem;font-size:0.8rem;color:#4b5563;">Store in a cool, dry place. Keep out of reach of children. Consult a healthcare professional before use if you have any medical conditions.</p>
